{"tid":1419424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尋晚荃灣竟然衰係自己人手上","createTime":"2019-08-06T01:17:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T05:59:40.000Z","uid":11779,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"74e76e06a4264c10895775ee55de7bf6bfb93750","tid":1419424,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:17:48.000Z","msg":"大家同路人，但覺得和理非有和理非做，唔好干涉我地勇武 呢啲先係各自努力<br />\n希望今次當係教訓 唔好再多發生。唔想割蓆，因為我地都係兄弟 而兄第之間要互相尊重。"},{"pid":"7c8fa5084e3e69a081e9b605b1c9678b63df52b9","tid":1419424,"uid":11779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:20:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d6ccdd91f019be1f54e03506861f83f6d1e5b9e","tid":1419424,"uid":207087,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:40:44.000Z","msg":"對敵人仁慈=對自己殘忍"},{"pid":"e844e3efc573b2d6d87515d5a3de4b7eecbaf6f2","tid":1419424,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d6ccdd91f019be1f54e03506861f83f6d1e5b9e","tid":1419424,"uid":207087,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:40:44.000Z","msg":"對敵人仁慈=對自己殘忍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:01:54.000Z","msg":"好sad"},{"pid":"43d9b7653a012edbf19ef17c21fbd47929184d6e","tid":1419424,"uid":264314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:02:16.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"5ad2022be5bb0e34f6cd0229cc5b186106ee9a91","tid":1419424,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74e76e06a4264c10895775ee55de7bf6bfb93750","tid":1419424,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:17:48.000Z","msg":"大家同路人，但覺得和理非有和理非做，唔好干涉我地勇武 呢啲先係各自努力<br />\n希望今次當係教訓 唔好再多發生。唔想割蓆，因為我地都係兄弟 而兄第之間要互相尊重。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:02:22.000Z","msg":"元朗都係"},{"pid":"c637b610dbd4b1ee4bee943074259af49c2e755f","tid":1419424,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:31:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">荃灣嗰班阻住同藍衫開拖既左膠們 你地依家開心啦:</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1418913/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1418913/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n唔撚洗屈我分化狗<br />\n<br />\n我就係企最前同藍衫對峙其中一位<br />\n明明遇藍衫之前講到明<br />\n勇武既先好行前 立定野一定打硬<br />\n<br />\n一遇藍衫 本身都準備打<br />\n就有兩個死廢物衝最前伸大雙手叫人唔好打<br />\n趕走佢地就算<br />\n然後一少部分人又和應<br />\n最後趕狗趕到力生廣場後少少就叫大家唔好追<br />\n準備轉場<br />\n<br />\n我最記得有個垃圾主動講<br />\n我地唔可以主動出手 只可以還拖<br />\n<br />\n行去地鐵站途中 後面就比人偷雞<br />\n跑返去已經見到first aid圍住<br />\n藍衫又走曬<br />\n行到死搵曬成個荃灣都冇影<br />\n<br />\n就係你班道德撚累到位手足爆頭<br />\n佔個道德高地 換黎自己友犠牲 屌你老母<br />\n你地醒未呀<br />\n<br />\n我真係想知你地咩心態<br />\n你地知道有手足比人爆頭嗰刻 <br />\n自己會唔會罪惡感<br />\n位手足既傷完全就係你地既偽善罪證<br />\n<br />\n我最後要同所有道德撚講<br />\n我唔會再犯下同樣錯誤<br />\n下次再有道德撚衝出黎阻自己人<br />\n我會撲低你地 唔會再比你地害自己友<br />\n等其他人實踐真正勇武 保護自己人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">荃灣黑社會追打義士同記者，再被反攻全紀錄</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/520Y9G4ao-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F520Y9G4ao-A&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKahYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=6110dbf3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/520Y9G4ao-A</a>"},{"pid":"17e17eca269c9f91212dc1ee66a6d7cfecc65118","tid":1419424,"uid":276548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:33:07.000Z","msg":"以後見到左膠阻人 <br />\n先警告 沒效 <br />\n再把他索起"},{"pid":"45efa2d085df704c637bff5be5362b27000844d4","tid":1419424,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:39:26.000Z","msg":"叫和理非收皮啦<br />\n<br />\n打又唔打得，一味搞到市民捱黑社會刀<br />\n<br />\n成事不足，敗事有餘"},{"pid":"afe4659170fc66dc7ad14773a1e293f68607cd98","tid":1419424,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17e17eca269c9f91212dc1ee66a6d7cfecc65118","tid":1419424,"uid":276548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:33:07.000Z","msg":"以後見到左膠阻人 <br />\n先警告 沒效 <br />\n再把他索起"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:40:11.000Z","msg":"左膠有D唔蒙面, 舉高雙手係前面攔<br />\n<br />\n有D蒙面<br />\n<br />\n左膠通常3個人一組行動"},{"pid":"189c42fb62499d4252ad06c0cbd6acb9f3a11161","tid":1419424,"uid":145496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e844e3efc573b2d6d87515d5a3de4b7eecbaf6f2","tid":1419424,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d6ccdd91f019be1f54e03506861f83f6d1e5b9e","tid":1419424,"uid":207087,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:40:44.000Z","msg":"對敵人仁慈=對自己殘忍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:01:54.000Z","msg":"好sad"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:53:21.000Z","msg":"慢慢黎，總有人進步得慢"},{"pid":"1af26d1461d18fd22cdd2ef06e9a63e2408f6f78","tid":1419424,"uid":140127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:54:05.000Z","msg":"繼「不分化、不篤灰、不割蓆」同埋Be Water後抗爭新原則<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1420765\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1420765</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1e8ec8707efbc96bba12367eec0a19d6d5da6be4","tid":1419424,"uid":29581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:59:40.000Z","msg":"真心on9 <br />\n你問班左膠 對面班人就斬死你嘅時候會唔會有佢地自己友衝出黎叫住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好斬啦 唔好斬啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n放生佢地 只會令自己手足成為下一個目標 <br />\n佢地欺善怕惡 只會惡過佢地 打撚到殘廢 佢地就唔會再出黎 唔該下次再有呢種情況 搵人帶返佢去後面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}